results.description:
내 머리를 혼란에 빠뜨리는 막막하고 막연한 단어 공부. 그 해답을 찾기 위해 제 영혼의 단짝인 디자이너와 함께 머리를 맞대고 끝없는 사투를 벌인 끝에 재미있는 녀석을 만들었습니다. 어때요, 우리와 함께해보지 않을래요?



외우면 까먹고 외우면 까먹고.. 아무리 외워도 오래 지난 단어는 까먹고 또 까먹고.. 이제는 걱정 말아요. 원보카와 함께라면 아무리 오래 된 단어도 항상 기억할 수 있어요. 매섭고 매정한 원보카는 우리가 최근에 외운 쉬운 문제만 내 줄 생각이 없어요. 언제 어떤 단어가 나타날지 예측할 수 없답니다.
하지만 원보카가 호랑이 선생이 된 데에는 다 이유가 있죠. 그건 바로 여러분이 단어를 암기하기 위해 원보카에 단어를 등록 했던 그 의지를 하나하나 친절하게 기억하고 그 꿈을 이루어 주기 위해 매를 들고 있는, 사실은 여러분을 지극히 아끼고 사랑하는 서포터이며 선생님입니다. :) 이제 우리 원보카 선생님과 함께, 잊어버릴 일 없는 든든한 단어 공부를 시작해 볼까요?



► 학습 지원 언어
영어 단어 뿐만이 아닌 다양한 외국어, 의학, 역사 외에도 갖가지 다양한 단어, 문장 그 모든 걸 공부할 수 있도록 고안 된 나만의 단어장.  

► 다양한 학습 기능 
최고의 학습 효율을 위한 군더더기 없는 깔끔하고 근본 있는(강조) 다양한 학습 기능 제안. 

► 함께 공부하기 
친구 또는 스터디 그룹 팀원과 함께 합심하여 공부할 수 있는 단어 공유 서비스. 

► TTS (Text To Speech)
어색함 없는 이 세대 최고의 언어 인공지능 비서가 네이티브한 발음으로 읽어주는 TTS. 



앱이 마음에 드신다면 리뷰를 남겨주세요. 문제 또는 피드백이 있으신 경우 앱 내 문의하기 또는 개발자 이메일로 연락해주세요. 리뷰를 이용한 피드백은 대기 시간이 무척이나 길기 때문에 리뷰 보다는 개발자 메일로 직접 이야기 해 주시면 훨씬 더 빠른 답변을 받아보실 수 있습니다. 원보카는 언제 어디서나 여러분들의 의견을 애타게 기다리고 있습니다. :)

results.description:
TinyTERM Enterprise for iOS combines secure terminal emulation with highly configurable keyboards to allow creation and deployment of purpose-based and scanning devices requiring access to legacy hosts or HTML 5/Javascript application in modern mobile environments.

The included secure SSH, SSL, and telnet IBM/VT/ANSI/Wyse/ADDS terminal emulation provides macros, printing and automation capabilities with scanner support.  TinyTERM Enterprise provides enterprise deployment capabilities including configuration push, user interface lockdown and extensive configuration import/export management.

TinyTERM’s industrial browser includes comprehensive scanning capabilities for scanning bar codes into input fields, redirecting QR scan codes to web pages and full compatibility with Safari.

The Scandit software-based barcode scanner provides lightning-fast scanning speed to power today’s enterprise-grade solutions.  Scandit’s precision scanning performs in the most adverse of conditions, such as low lighting, glare and warped surfaces, and works with all major 1D and 2D barcode symbologies.  TinyTERM Enterprise includes a 14-day trial of the Scandit software barcode scanner solution for evaluation.

Features

• Display custom keyboards automatically based on screen content
• Keyboard swipe of custom keyboards
• Customer requested enhancements added for pre-sales requirements
• Secure SSH, SSL and telnet access over WiFi, cellular and VPN networks
• Comprehensive RSA/DSA key generation and management with key export
• SSL Host certificate authentication
• Multiple session support
• Japanese, Korean & Chinese support 
• User interface customization including no title bar, lock down
• Onscreen UI for remapping keys to actions, macros and character strings
• Configuration import/export with multiple configuration package file wrapping
• .tpx adjustable connection time-out
• TE Proxy server
• Split View support
• Application display can be precisely configured for each keyboard mode in both landscape and portrait orientations
• External Bluetooth/dock keyboards supported with function, arrow & control keys
• Industrial scanning browser with HTML5 & javascript execution 
• Phone & email technical support

Keyboard Layouts

• Transparent keyboard option for continuous full screen visibility
• Fully customizable keyboards – generate layouts to meet needs
• Configurable onscreen PC, VT and IBM-style keyboards with & without fn keys
• Custom programmable keyboards in VT220, IBM3151, numeric 10-key and PC 101-key English, Spanish, French, German, Norwegian layouts

Printing

• Text screen and host transparent print to AirPrint and email

Automation

• Macro record/playback to automate connecting and host application startup
• Macro can prompt for username/password or store separately in connection info
• Auto-connect on start allows one-touch connectivity from home screen
• Auto-login on connect associates macro with connect/login sequence
• Auto-reconnect re-establishes connection and auto-login if dropped
• Prevent disconnect enforces proper host system/application logoff
• Close on disconnect for quick exit

Software Scanning Support

• Scandit
• Software scanner using camera

Scanner Support

• Cognex
• Honeywell
• Infinite Peripherals
• Bluetooth devices

Terminals Emulated:

ADDS: Viewpoint, 60, A2
Alpha Micro: WYCOL/Esprit III
ANSI: ANSI 3.64, SCOANSI, AT386, Linux Console
Digital: VT100, VT220, VT220-7, VT320, VT320-7, VT420
IBM: TN3270E Models 2-5, TN5250 Models 3179-2/3477-FC/5555-C01, 3151, 3101
Wyse/TVI: Wyse 50, Wyse 60, Wyse 60-25, Televideo 912, 925, 950
Other: ATT 4410, ADM1, PCTERM, TTY

Application display can be precisely configured for each keyboard mode in both landscape and portrait orientations.

Thank you for your valuable comments.  Please email support@censoft.com with any feedback.

LibTerm is a command line interface for iPhone and iPad. Includes what you need for coding C programs!

Commands:

ls, lli, ifconfig, ping, readlink, id, chmod, clang, telnet, host, du, link, dig, egrep, bc, date, gzip, nslookup, python2, fgrep, mv, python3, md5, say, luac, ssh-keygen, xargs, diff, cd, tee, chksum, lua, touch, dc, tar, chflags, rm, sort, uniq, awk, printenv, chgrp, find, mkdir, tail, df, pwd, opt, chown, gunzip, compress, llvm-link, nc, uptime, sed, setenv, stat, uname, sum, head, wc, cat, echo, unsetenv, unlink, pbpaste, rmdir, uncompress, curl, ln, cp, whoami, rlogin, tr, env, whois, pbcopy, python, grep, nm, jsc, clear, sh, help, exit, open, package, edit

Edit text files and code with a graphical editor and syntax highlighting with the 'edit' command.

Not enough commands? You can code your own scripts with Python 2.7, Python 3.7, Lua 5.3, install third party commands or even compile and run C code with the 'clang' and 'lli' commands!

This application is the most convenient way to keep track of your labor contractions. I created this application for use during my own wife's labor and have paid special attention to keeping the interface as clean and clutter free as possible. 

You have to tap a single button to track the start and end of each of your contractions, and "Full Term" will take care of the rest. The application is designed to keep track of the times, durations and frequency of the entire labor period. 

Your full labor history and contraction progress will be saved regardless of whether you restart the application during a contraction or restart the entire device. There is no need to keep this application open the whole time. Of course, you can also email your contraction history to a health care professional or for your records.

In addition, you get a full featured Fetal Kick counter and a handy pregnancy reference section that you can use to brush up your knowledge.

To summarize, some of the features are:

Contraction Timer
* Simple interface to track each contraction
* View your complete contraction history in chronological or reverse chronological order
* Edit your contractions in case you forget
* Manually enter contraction entries if needed
* Undo your contractions in case you make a mistake
* Setup Contraction Alerts based on the 5-1-1 rule or customize to suit your needs 
* Track breaking of waters
* Add a note to any contraction
* Specify the intensity of each contraction
* Monitor your labor progression using the built-in graphs
* Apple Watch Support

Kick Counter
* Full Featured Kick counter
* View your complete Kick count session history
* Setup Reminders to make sure you count kicks at the same time every day!
* Email Kick counting history
* Customize the session length or the number of kicks counted per session
* Edit your Kick counting session by deleting accidental entries
* Add a note to any Kick counting session

Weight Tracker
* Track your weight gain progress through your Pregnancy
* Enter Due date information to Weight Gain for Pregnancy Week
* Attach notes to each weight entry
* Setup reminders to take your weight at the same time each week

* Great reference section included to provide pregnancy information

* Backup your history to iCloud
* Resume timing your labor on another device connected to the same iCloud account
* Configure the duration to monitor and determine trends
* Email your contraction history to anyone
* Dark Theme Mode for use in low light conditions to decrease eye strain

영국, 호주, 캐나다, 이탈리아 등에서 1위! ***

이것은 사용하기에 가장 간단한 출산 도우미 앱 입니다. 
이 앱은 당신의 수축 시간을 기록하여 언제 병원에 가야하는 지 알려줍니다.
만약 집에서 출산을 계획하고 계신다면, 이 앱은 출산 과정 단계를 모든 순간에 알려줍니다.

수축이 일어날 때와 끝날 때 하나의 버튼을 누름으로써 출산 과정을 기록하세요. 이 출산 도우미 앱은 수축 기간과 빈도를 분석한 후 언제 병원에 가야하는 지 알려줍니다.  

전 세계의 수 천명의 임산부들이 저희 앱을 사용하여 엄마들이 되었습니다.

수축 빈도와 기간에 따른 결정은 언제나 의사와 상담하세요.
이 앱은 의학적 기기가 아니며 저희는 표준 형식에 따라 안내합니다. 당신의 출산은 다르게 나타날 수도 있습니다. 따라서, 저희 앱 만에 의존하지 마십시오.
만약 수축 빈도와 기간이 필요한 표준과 일치하지 않고 고통이 참을 수 없는 수준에 이르면, 집에서 출산하거나 도중에 출산하는 것 보다 최대한 빨리 병원에 가시는 것이 좋습니다. 당신의 몸이 말하는 대로 따르세요.

끊어찍기, 확대, 배속 등 다양한 카메라 기능을 통해 누구나 손쉽게 사건사고 현장을 더욱 실감나게 촬영할 수 있어요.

[거기어때?]
'틈(TERM)'의 '거기어때?' 서비스는 궁금한 위치의 질문을 남기고, 영상으로 답변 받는 서비스입니다. 이제 실감나는 실황 영상으로 궁금증을 해소하세요!

[제보자 리워드]
제보자에겐 제보 콘텐츠의 인기도(조회수 등)와 비례한 리워드가 주어집니다. 우수 제보자를 선정하는 명예 시상식도 개최할 예정이랍니다!

[카테고리와 시청 등급]
제보 콘텐츠를 카테고리 별로 구분하여 업로드하거나 시청할 수 있어요. 제보할 때에는 콘텐츠의 시청 등급을 직접 지정할 수도 있답니다.

[익명제보와 댓글 끄기]
'틈(TERM)'은 제보자의 권리 보호를 위해 노력합니다. '틈(TERM)' 이용자라면 누구나 익명제보 기능과 댓글 OFF 기능을 사용할 수 있습니다.

언제, 어디서나 '틈(TERM)'만 있다면
여러분의 제보가 세상을 놀라게 할 수 있습니다!


The fastest way to view video of an accident is TERM

Shoot and report the events that happen around you, the disasters, the daily lives, and so on. As soon as you run TERM, you'll be able to see the issues in the world the fastest.

In the main view, you can check out the most popular video and the most recent video clip. Check out the world's issues faster than anyone else!

Through various camera functions such as cutting, zooming, and distributing, anyone can easily take pictures of the accident scene.

[Hot Place]

The informant is given a reward in proportion to the popularity(e.g. number of hits) of the informational content. We will also hold an honorary award ceremony to select the best informants!

[Categories and Video Ratings]
You can upload or watch contents by category. When reporting, you can also rate the contents directly.

Whenever and wherever with TERM,

results.releaseNotes: We are working hard to bring you digital products that change your life as a tenant. This new version contains bug fixes and performance improvements.
results.description:
Our goal is to help people spend time on what they love. That’s why Spotahome lets you rent homes without seeing them in person. Picture yourself viewing thousands of rooms for rent in flatshares from the comfort of your sofa. Imagine using your smartphone to visit 20 apartments for rent in just one hour. Now, all of this is possible - the hunt for housing has never been easier or safer.

We check properties so you don’t have to. We create listings that are so accurate that you can book your next home without having to visit it in person.

How does it work?

We send our Homecheckers to the properties that we list on our platform. The Homechecker takes high-quality photos, 360° images, accurate floor plans, and professional video tours of each property. Their material is then sent to our Copywriters who describe everything from the interior of the living room, right down to the vibe of the local neighbourhood. The end result is a virtual viewing that’s just as realistic as an in-person visit.

We know that it’s important for you to find the right landlord. That’s why we include practical information about landlord policies, utilities, tenant preferences and house rules. That way, landlords and tenants both know that they are the right fit for each other.

We are working hard to bring you digital products that change your life as a tenant. That’s why we improve and update our product on a daily basis.

Used by tens of thousands of health professionals worldwide. Purchase includes access to the official Tabers.com website

ABOUT TABER'S MEDICAL DICTIONARY:
Find the critical medical information you need quickly and easily, wherever you need it. Taber’s is the leading medical dictionary used by health care professionals today. 

Taber’s Medical Dictionary contains over 65,000 terms, 1,200 photos, 32,000 audio pronunciations, 100+ videos, and more than 600 Patient Care Statements from the latest edition. Taber’s goes beyond the in-depth definitions and provides nutrition and alternative therapy, medical abbreviations, symbols and units of measurement, immunization schedules, nursing diagnoses, and updates.

Plus, you’ll have access to the full dictionary, illustrations, audio pronunciations, and more at the Taber's website. 

FEATURES:
• 65,000+ in-depth definitions 
• 1,200+ high-quality images and 100+ videos 
• Nearly 32,000 audio pronunciations
• Useful appendices with Laboratory Values, Alternative Medicine, and more 
• Enhanced Search help you find topics quickly
• Favorites for ‘bookmarking’ important entries
• Highlight and make notes within any entry
• Free: 1-year of web access to the official Taber's website
